{"tid":778001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇大學生而家返緊份intern係咁","createTime":"2018-08-13T11:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T14:33:22.000Z","uid":188688,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3a92de9461ac5e5fc6d92f6b84b38c2d2dd61e1c","tid":778001,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"我今年升year2 揾左份返office嘅intern 睇佢係大公司 人工又唔錯咁 就accept咗<br />\n<br />\n我問過係做乜 佢就話係文書嗰啲<br />\n咁我諗住唔多唔少都會學到吓嘢 例如部門運作咁<br />\n<br />\n點知一返工 發現我要做嘅嘢只係不停咁重複做某幾個動作 <br />\n我唔方便講細節 但係真係好撚簡單<br />\n唔使用腦都做到 <br />\n不過啲full time唔會嘥時間做先請個intern返嚟做咁解<br />\n<br />\n悶都預咗 但係真係完全學唔到嘢 <br />\n講真 我寧願無人工而有嘢學到<br />\n至少講得返比人聽我做過乜<br />\n而家諗住如果要話返啲工作經驗比人知 就空泛啲講返我做文書嘢算數<br />\n<br />\n諗返起真係留喺屋企自學啲技能好過<br />\n而家做到眼都矇撚埋添"},{"pid":"3dc8f8d0519f6bd9f6d50bf21b4d6ed8703e23da","tid":778001,"uid":34084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"資料輸入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4dfa23a7f479b24c5ac72f9f4e015af21e3364","tid":778001,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc8f8d0519f6bd9f6d50bf21b4d6ed8703e23da","tid":778001,"uid":34084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"資料輸入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"嗰類嘢 總之係好機械式的"},{"pid":"2581bee7159d797fea7752e699848c633e002129","tid":778001,"uid":62167,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"教完你做一兩個月就走，教黎拓。就算你返full time都會發現班senior keep住一D野唔會教你。"},{"pid":"fb2857cf375fe99bb84d235134560d804fcfe166","tid":778001,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c4dfa23a7f479b24c5ac72f9f4e015af21e3364","tid":778001,"uid":188688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc8f8d0519f6bd9f6d50bf21b4d6ed8703e23da","tid":778001,"uid":34084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1